name: レイナ - Leina Vance Queen's Blade / クイーンズブレイド
description:
31th Release, レイナ - Leina Vance From Queen's Blade - クイーンズブレイド.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Character's Request.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 134+ Images that i sorted manually, at the max quality possible (Orginal Art 4K + Official Art 4K), Were used in the datasets) SFW+NFSW.

  • Can do Official Default Skin, Somewhat precisely.

  • Flexibility is Ok/Good.

  • Can do Original Art.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Work's Perfectly at Weight 1.

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it).

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Ok/Good (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: LeinaV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.7-1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned Blue Eyes, Blonde Hair, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((Blue Eyes, Blonde Hair)) prompt.

For default skin, put 0.7-1 Weight, See examples Image for this.

For Flexibility for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

Buckle + Gauntlet are Inconsitent, Idk why, but you can try to force it with ((Buckle, Gauntlet)) prompt.

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Prompt.
